# GIAC-E01: chain rule case; answer is Giac, native steps are agreement-gated.
wait 200
open_app Calculus
wait 60
key sin
key x
key RIGHT
key ^
key 2
key ENTER
wait 120
assert_calculus_engine giac
assert_calculus_operation differentiate
assert_calculus_status ok
assert_calculus_result_kind structured
assert_calculus_result_exact 2*cos(x)*sin(x)
assert_calculus_tutor_status agreed
